A [[dog]] [[wash]] is an establishment where one takes their canine pet to be cleaned and groomed.

Dogwash is also a [[slang]] term meaning a project one does in place of another, higher priority task, e.g. washing the dog instead of paying bills. It is a method of [[procrastination]] that alleviates [[guilt]] by creating the illusion of [[productivity]].

Its source is unknown.